description:
Jessada Sutthi attended Udonthani Rajabhat University 2004-2007 and received a Bachelor of Art - Major Visual Communication Art Design. Originally he was a freelance artist on a small game concept, book cover and took part in Devacurse card games project (2007). He later joined The Monk Studio as a matte painter for TV animations (2008-2009). He then moved to Anya Animation Studio to work on concept art and matte painting in the animation series called The Lady of Badal (2009-2010). He then went back to work as a freelancer, providing matte painting and concept arts for various animations and TV advertisements. Currently he is a senior concept artist for Studio HIVE in 2011 and became Art Director in 2012.

http://jessada-art.deviantart.com/
name: Jessada Sutthi
